date>
<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Tebtynis</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Αὐρή<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">λιο</supplied>ς Σαραπίων Πωλίωνι 

    <lb n="2"/>τῷ ἀδελφῷ καὶ Διογέ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear>ι 

    <lb n="3"/>τῷ πατρὶ <choice><corr>πλεῖστα</corr><sic>πλειστοι</sic></choice> χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="4"/>οἴδατε ὅτι ἀπὸ ζημίας <choice><corr>εἰμὶ</corr><sic>ημι</sic></choice> καὶ 

    <lb n="5"/><choice><corr>ἀλόγως</corr><sic>αλογος</sic></choice> ἐξήλθατε ἀπ᾽ ἐμοῦ μὴ 

    <lb n="6"/><choice><corr>δόντες</corr><sic>δουντες</sic></choice> μοι χάλκινα. ἠγόρ-

    <lb n="7"/>ασα <num value="2">β</num> χάρτας εἰς τοὺς σωμα-

    <lb n="8"/>τισμοὺς τῶν σιτικῶν τοῦ βασιλι-

    <lb n="9"/>κοῦ καὶ <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="28">κη</num> ὑπὲρ συμφωνίας 

    <lb n="10"/>τῆς <choice><corr>ἀβρ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ό</supplied>χου</corr><sic>αβρχω</sic></choice> αὐτῷ <choice><corr>πάλιν</corr><sic>παλειν</sic></choice> τῷ βασι-

    <lb n="11"/>λικῷ. πάντα οὖν ποιήσατε ὡς 

    <lb n="12"/><choice><corr>ἂν</corr><sic>εν</sic></choice> ἀνάγκης οὔσης πέμψατέ μοι 

    <lb n="13"/>τὰς ἐμὰς <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="52">νβ</num>· καὶ συνλέξατε καὶ <choice><corr>ὑμεῖς</corr><sic>ημις</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="14"/>εἰς τὸν ἐμὸν λό<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">γ</supplied>ον ἄλλα<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς</supplied> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="60">ξ</num>, ἐπὶ γὰρ 

    <lb n="15"/><choice><corr>χρείαν</corr><sic>χρηαν</sic></choice> ἔχω <gap reason="lost" extent="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ην</unclear> μέση ποεῖται. 

    <lb n="16"/>ἀναγ<g type="apostrophe"/>καίως οὖν, κύριέ μου ἀδελφὲ 

    <lb n="17"/>Πωλίων, μνήσθητί μου <choice><corr>ὃ</corr><sic>ον</sic></choice> καὶ <choice><corr>ἐγὼ</corr><sic>καγω</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="18"/>πεποίηκά σοι ἀπὸ ἀρχῆς μέχρι τέ-

    <lb n="19"/>λους καὶ πάλιν <choice><corr>σοι</corr><sic>σαι</sic></choice> ὑπηρετῶ. παρακά-

    <lb n="20"/><choice><corr>λεσόν</corr><sic>παρεκαλησαν</sic></choice> μου τὸν ἀδελφὸν <sic>τον α</sic> ὥστε 

    <lb n="21"/>πρὸς <choice><corr>σὲ</corr><sic>σαι</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ἐλθεῖν</corr><sic>ελθιν</sic></choice> ἕνεκα τῶν κριθαρ-

    <lb n="22"/>ίων καὶ <choice><corr>μετάδος</corr><sic>μεταδες</sic></choice> Διογένι ἵνα καὶ 

    <lb n="23"/>αὐτὸς <choice><corr>δοῖ</corr><sic>δυ</sic></choice> ἀρτάβην κριθῆς εἰς λό-

    <lb n="24"/>γον ὀψωνίων. δὸς οὖν τὴν ὀνήν 

    <lb n="25"/>σου ἵνα ἀνασπασθῇ ἀναγ<g type="apostrophe"/>καίως, 

    <lb n="26"/>ἐπὶ γὰρ κατάκλειστός <choice><corr>εἰμι</corr><sic>ημι</sic></choice> μέχ-

    <lb n="27"/>ρι <choice><corr>σήμερο<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ν</supplied></corr><sic>σημερο</sic></choice> ἐν τῷ λογιστηρίῳ, 

    <lb n="28"/>καὶ δήλωσόν μοι ἀναγ<g type="apostrophe"/>καίως 

    <lb n="29"/>περί μου τί ἔ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">πρ</unclear>αξας. <expan>ἐρρῶσθ<ex cert="high">αι</ex></expan> <expan>εὔχο<ex cert="high">μαι</ex></expan>. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="30"/><gap reason="lost" extent="8" unit="character"/>ον τῷ ἀδελφῷ σοι <expan>Σαραπί<ex cert="high">ων</ex></expan>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.31364" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.31364" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="201" notAfter="300">III</date></p></div><div n="meta.31364" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Vgl. Kruse, Der Königliche Schreiber, S. 1093-1102.</p></div><div n="meta.31364" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Tebt.</title><biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">420</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">31364</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0206</series>; <biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">420</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0206;2;420" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.31364" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.31364" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot" cert="high" full="yes">Tebtynis</placeName> (<geogName type="nome" cert="high" full="yes">Arsinoites</geogName>), <geogName type="ancientRegion" key="Aegyptus" cert="high" full="yes">Egypt</geogName></p></div><div n="meta.31364" type="figure" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><figure href="http://wwwapp.cc.columbia.edu/ldpd/app/apis/item?mode=item&amp;key=berkeley.apis.302"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet<